Pipe operator

Source: R/utils.R
pipe.Rd

Exported from the magrittr package. To learn more, run ?magrittr::`%>%`.

lhs %>% rhs

Examples

mtcars %>%
  tabyl(carb, cyl) %>%
  adorn_totals()
#>   carb  4 6  8
#>      1  5 2  0
#>      2  6 0  4
#>      3  0 0  3
#>      4  0 4  6
#>      6  0 1  0
#>      8  0 0  1
#>  Total 11 7 14
